  characterName: Oscar
  lines:
  - Wonderful! I can already see the improvments we are about to make.
  - Much like last time, let me share some secrets with you about Artificial Intelligence.
  - '[LEARNING CONTENT HERE]'
  - Oh! Before I forget, since you've helped us out so much, take this badge. I am
    sure others around here are in need of some help and you'll need that to get
    around.
  - Everyone you help will give you some information about Artificial Intelligence
    in return. Thanks again!
